{"lastModified":1775206552962,"uri":"c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc79f2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Australia, Queensland, Cairns, New South Wales, Sydney\n\nEVOLUTION presents itself as a breathtaking vessel that never fails to captivate its guests. Externally, it exudes modern elegance, boasting a custom-made wide staircase connecting the upper and main decks, along with various entertainment and relaxation spots such as a sunbed lounge, a foredeck lounge area with a removable sun awning, and a sleek aft bar area. Inside, the luxury only amplifies, with a chic and minimalist interior reminiscent of a sophisticated Manhattan penthouse.\n\nThe yacht features multiple entertainment zones equipped with state-of-the-art systems.\n\nAccommodation includes a master cabin, two VIP cabins, and a double cabin, each offering the epitome of comfort and luxury.\n\nNoteworthy features include a custom-made floating king-size bed in the master cabin, a 7 x 5 meter inflatable freedom pool, and a fully equipped dive tank room. Moreover, EVOLUTION provides stand-up paddleboards and an underwater scooter for added leisure. The yacht also boasts a 4-meter swim platform extension, offering additional space for recreational activities.\n\nAdditionally, all furniture aboard EVOLUTION is designed for multi-functional use, ensuring versatile dining and lounging areas for guests to enjoy.","blueprint":{"name":"EVOLUTION","images":["/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc79f2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d62e18b0-e688-11ee-8cba-afbca4cb7e72.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc79f2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::cebfef90-e688-11ee-8cba-afbca4cb7e72.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc79f2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d7ddc480-e688-11ee-8cba-afbca4cb7e72.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc79f2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43